thread.title: U.S. and at least 15 European states expel Russian diplomats

title: U.S. and at least 15 European states expel Russian diplomats
text:
U.S. and at least 15 European states expel Russian diplomats 10:17am EDT - 01:04 
Senior Trump administration officials have confirmed the expulsion of 60 Russians and closing of the Seattle consulate, as NATO and E.U. member states announce similar expulsions in the wake of the Sergei Skripal incident.
